title: New Creator Prop: 6AM Group
body:
Name: 6AM Group

Socials:
https://www.6amgroup.com/
https://twitter.com/6amgroup
https://www.instagram.com/6amgroup/
https://www.facebook.com/6amGroup/

About: 
6AM is an experiential and digital media platform covering all facets of underground electronic music culture, resource, technology, and lifestyle. Following our humble beginnings as a Los Angeles-based local blog and club sub-promotion company, we have since seen our global outreach, industry experience, scope and knowledge expand exponentially with each passing year. 
As of today, we have organized and promoted over 1,000 events, ranging from festivals and warehouse events, to mega-clubs, intimate lounges and unique outdoor venues. 
Aside from producing events, we have helped dozens of music artists, festivals, music labels, pro-audio companies, and consumer-facing businesses reach our target demographic and ultimately “get their word out.” thanks to the digital marketing, social media, and native promotion skills we have honed in through our years of experience in the nightlife and entertainment industry. 
In May of 2019 we went a step further, launching a fully-fledged techno + house apparel and merchandise Shop by 6AM. 

Distribution Plan: 
We will be using our $RAVE coins as incentives for our most loyal supporters via our events and shop purchases. We plan on running contests to include the $RAVE coin as added incentive as well as include them as part of our special merchandise drops. When events return, we plan to reward attendees as well.

Holding Mechanics: 
$RAVE coin holders will be put on a special list where they get offered exclusive discounts and access to our merch, first-notice of events before they are announced. 
Holding $RAVE coins and showing proof at our future events may grant them discounted entry and merch at the show. 

Transactions: 
We will incentivize our fans to use these $RAVE coins for purchases of merch and event tickets, and are exploring exclusive streaming opportunities for $RAVE.

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1000

A 'yes' will approve this proposal and provide a $1000 gift coin grant

A 'no' will deny this prop
